dow jones
the nevada public utilities commission wednesday voted to allow its general counsel office to take any action necessary to try to void or renegotiate long-term electricity contracts entered into by the state's two largest utilities
a puc spokeswoman said
the contracts would force sierra pacific resources
srp
utilities sierra pacific power co
and nevada power co
